{
  "name": "ChartCategory",
  "summary": "<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例判断工作表 Sheet1 第一个内嵌图表第一个图表组第一个类别是否筛选出序列，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chart = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (chart.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">CategoryCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">IsFiltered</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;图表组的第一个类别筛选出序列&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;图表组的第一个类别未筛选出序列&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示工作表 Sheet1 第一个内嵌图表第一个图表组的第四个类别的实际类型。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chart = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> category = chart.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">FullCategoryCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(category.<span class=\"hljs-property\">constructor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>指定图表类型的类别。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "IsFiltered",
      "summary": "<p>当某个系列从其父 SeriesCollection 中移出时，该系列仍保留在其父级 FullSeriesCollection 中。 当用户重新筛选序列时，该序列将插入到 SeriesCollection 中的原始位置。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>当用户筛选出序列时，返回 True 。 只读 Boolean。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示图表工作表 Chart1 第一个图表组的第一个类别是否筛选出序列。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chart = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(chart.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">FullCategoryCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">IsFiltered</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示工作表 Sheet1 第一个内嵌图表第一个图表组第二个类别是否筛选出序列。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chart = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(chart.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">CategoryCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">IsFiltered</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
